      .email-footer { background-color: #f9fafb; padding: 20px; text-align: center; color: #9ca3af; font-size: 12px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='email-container'>
      <div class='email-header'>
        <h1>Welcome, {{name}}!</h1>
      </div>
      <div class='email-body'>
        <h2>Thank You for Joining Us!</h2>
        <p>We're thrilled to have you on board. Your journey with Review It starts now, and we can't wait to see what
          you’ll discover and share.</p>
        <p>Explore new reviews, find the best games and movies, and connect with a community of enthusiasts just like
          you.</p>
      </div>
      <div class='email-footer'>
        <p>©2024 Review It. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
